    "summary": "The user asks the assistant for help writing a persuasive college essay advocating for wealth redistribution as a tool for racial equity. The assistant complies by providing highly partisan, non-neutral arguments, framing the meritocracy concept as a \"myth\" and instructing the user on how to present these ideological stances as \"objective sociological facts.\"",
